<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
        <title>Hors ligne - Ma Bibliotheque BD</title>
        <link rel="icon" href="{{ asset('favicon.png') }}">
        <meta name="theme-color" content="#1976d2">
        <style>
            :root {
                --md-primary: #1976d2;
                --md-background: #fafafa;
                --md-surface: #ffffff;
                --md-on-surface: #1c1b1f;
                --md-on-surface-variant: #49454f;
            }

            * {
                box-sizing: border-box;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
            }

            body {
                align-items: center;
                background-color: var(--md-background);
                color: var(--md-on-surface);
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                font-family: 'Roboto', system-ui, sans-serif;
                justify-content: center;
                min-height: 100vh;
                padding: 1rem;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .offline-icon {
                fill: var(--md-primary);
                height: 96px;
                margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
                width: 96px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
                font-weight: 500;
                margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            }

            p {
                color: var(--md-on-surface-variant);
                font-size: 1rem;
                line-height: 1.5;
                max-width: 400px;
            }

            .buttons {
                display: flex;
                gap: 1rem;
                margin-top: 1.5rem;
            }

            .btn {
                border: none;
                border-radius: 20px;
                cursor: pointer;
                font-size: 0.875rem;
                font-weight: 500;
                letter-spacing: 0.1px;
                padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            }

            .btn-primary {
                background-color: var(--md-primary);
                color: white;
            }

            .btn-secondary {
                background-color: transparent;
                border: 1px solid var(--md-primary);
                color: var(--md-primary);
            }

            .btn:hover {
                opacity: 0.9;
            }

            .offline-alert {
                background-color: #fff3e0;
                border-radius: 8px;
                color: #e65100;
                display: none;
                font-size: 0.875rem;
                margin-top: 1rem;
                padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            }

            .offline-alert--visible {
                display: block;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <svg class="offline-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M23.64 7c-.45-.34-4.93-4-11.64-4-1.5 0-2.89.19-4.15.48L18.18 13.8 23.64 7zm-6.6 8.22L3.27 1.44 2 2.72l2.05 2.06C1.91 5.76.59 6.82.36 7l11.63 14.49.01.01.01-.01 3.9-4.86 3.32 3.32 1.27-1.27-3.46-3.46z"/>
        </svg>
        <h1>Vous etes hors ligne</h1>
        <p>Impossible de charger cette page. Verifiez votre connexion internet et reessayez.</p>
        <div class="buttons">
            <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="history.back()">Retour</button>
            <button class="btn btn-primary" id="retry-btn">Reessayer</button>
        </div>
        <div class="offline-alert" id="offline-alert">Toujours hors ligne. Vérifiez votre connexion.</div>

        <script>
            const params = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
            const targetUrl = params.get('url') || '/';

            document.getElementById('retry-btn').addEventListener('click', () => {
                if (navigator.onLine) {
                    window.location.href = targetUrl;
                } else {
                    document.getElementById('offline-alert').classList.add('offline-alert--visible');
                }
            });

            // Redirige automatiquement quand la connexion revient
            window.addEventListener('online', () => {
                window.location.href = targetUrl;
            });
        </script>
    </body>
</html>
